{"tid":779073,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港多唔多電競選手打到入世界賽/有排名?","createTime":"2018-08-14T07:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T05:12:10.000Z","uid":196632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0778c7e5e08eb73bf4bb6129eacef901cafb53","tid":779073,"uid":196632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"之前都有上網睇直播如:LOL世界冠軍賽, 台灣贏到總冠軍.<br />\n唔知幾時先有香港代表可以打贏世界賽."},{"pid":"37eca2bef9c34ca8441a7a90ad4bd8cc84af178a","tid":779073,"uid":52520,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔想吹奏佢  但冇toyz 冇tpa <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55688c38f0fd4c5b4afda6aacba0a926a97bb2c","tid":779073,"uid":195371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"其實香港都有唔少人玩LOL, 不過要成為職業選手真係好困難,<br />\n因為打機等於廢青呢個想法仍然根深柢固, 或者要有香港電競冠軍選手出現先的."},{"pid":"1f349c89b3ddbd886e2e26a68605f7f6d7c2a0a8","tid":779073,"uid":26066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"電競對於香港呢個注重金融同地產發展嘅地方其實好難搞，加上一般香港家庭都好反對自己仔女打機當職業，台灣同中國大陸一嚟地方大，二嚟政府肯支持，連台北市長都支持。<br />\n<br />\n其實同其他運動一樣，就好似足球咁，先唔講英超西甲嗰啲咁遠啦，日本，韓國，甚至中國都肯投資搞足球。球場，<br />\n、訓練場、領隊、教練，軍醫等等...... 都比香港好。有好嘅配置先有機會吸引人才。<br />\n<br />\n之前睇過一段Youtube 係訪問一個美國LOL選手 Doublelift ,我覺得佢講嘅嘢好啱，佢講到其實每一個地區都有一個Faker (韓國LOL傳奇），只不過係韓國人出色喺訓練同組織，去搵呢個 「Faker」出嚟，再將佢變成「神」"},{"pid":"3ddfc3dd223e7e556f5bd9a2dfa2a283aba7f11f","tid":779073,"uid":196511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"我地香港, 中國, 台灣, 韓國等都有唔少電競達人, 唔比外國選手差.<br />\n好似黎緊個電競音樂節都有三場國際級電競比賽, 都有香港代表.<br />\n比賽贏到有唔少獎金, 而且今屆D獎金亦創香港電競史上新高.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.emfhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emfhk.com&d=ZKH8qiq0938nELvGat%2FllLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6dbc2859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.emfhk.com</a>"},{"pid":"46c8a31b131ee8896ed78f6bf3211f1ba36a2e3d","tid":779073,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"deer chan"},{"pid":"0c966b46508f9cffa62e528d89d42b3f0ac93029","tid":779073,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"humanboom"},{"pid":"b466d6238624b9e89511a2d4e48bea3d9ce5a280","tid":779073,"uid":28041,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:30:13.000Z","msg":"Deer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8639d1c9d5a65bb7dea0e1f2307bcbf570fff35","tid":779073,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"hka隊lol仲有幾多個港仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a70c208df93826fc6508a2cf7ff69e01d83da8","tid":779073,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"Mk毒撚就自己摺埋打銅牌場算啦唔好再發夢，如果你係菁英頭正十名，咁都叫有d機"},{"pid":"7d7dec586aa51c391f71ff8e49c32611101e2a43","tid":779073,"uid":201054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"有無人會買飛入去睇? 上屆睇直播都好爽, 今屆D飛平左好多."},{"pid":"5cf3b1ba1811ea47e7d4af123a0d487de5e70f51","tid":779073,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"皇室戰爭有人攞亞洲冠軍"},{"pid":"a73b596910ed1076c4fef4fbaab62e82d40c5413","tid":779073,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"Deer chan囉 香港第一女子隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047f6fd40cd8130ed6ac17c9c0d5ca9296fc699d","tid":779073,"uid":196511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"會呀, 平平地$50買去睇下都好, 除左睇比賽仲可以去體驗專區,<br />\n試玩下新Game同VR,仲有Cosplay同網紅對決, 仲有音樂表現睇.<br />\n有時間仲可以去埋電腦節."},{"pid":"38848deeff8a41d41829998d1cecafbc2f5c237a","tid":779073,"uid":46390,"lik